WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to the Online Forklift Operator Certification Course.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
This comprehensive training program will prepare you for safe forklift operation
in compliance with OSHA standards.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
OSHA requires all forklift operators to receive proper training
and certification before operating powered industrial trucks.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Throughout this course, you will learn essential safety procedures,
pre-operation inspections, and proper operating techniques.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
You must successfully complete each module and pass all assessments
to receive your certification.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
This certification is valid for three years and demonstrates
your commitment to workplace safety.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Let's begin your journey to becoming a certified forklift operator.
Are you ready to start?

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Let's get started with your forklift safety training. 